The lady looked at the enthroned ones, but more at his consort than he. Maybe,
                     she was tempted to inquire if Master Ivan knew the girl also. But she did not;
                     women rarely let words escape that they afterwards would call back.

Fortunately, the cry of "Aux armes!" roused him
                  from his trance, and he hastened to tender military honors to the exiled King,
                  who, attended by one gentleman only, left the palace on foot.

